article:
About 8,000 Fellows have been elected to the Royal Society of London since its
inception in 1660. Below is a list of people who are or were Fellows or Foreign
Members of the Royal Society. The date of election to the Fellowship follows the
name. Dates in brackets relate to an award or event associated with the person.
The Society maintains complete online list. http://royalsociety.org/WorkAre-
a/DownloadAsset.aspx?id=4294972811 This list is complete up to and
including 2011.
